		<h2>ğŸ‘‡  Directions  ğŸ‘‡</h2>
	<div class="bullets">
		<ul>																                           <!-- Ordered list-->
			<li>In a large bowl, sift together the flour, baking powder, salt and sugar.ğŸ¥°</li>
			<li>Make a well in the center and pour in the milk, egg and melted butter.ğŸ•</li>
			<li>Mix until Smooth.ğŸ¥</li>
			<li>Heat a lightly oiled griddle or frying pan over medium high heat.ğŸ¥º</li>
			<li>Pour or scoop the batter onto the griddle, using approximately 1/4 cup for each pancake.â¤ï¸</li>
			<li>Brown on both sides and serve Hot.ğŸ”¥</li>
